thread.title: Alma Egan
thread.title_full: Fast Moves - Man With Van Dublin reviewed by Alma Egan

author: Alma Egan
title: Alma Egan
text: John has done a few moving jobs for me in the last year of a business and home move nature. On all occasions John arrived early and packed up and delivered efficiently and on time. As well as being well priced he was always a pleasure to deal with and I would recommend him wholeheartedly.
